{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"614cb5e6d2","title":"部队的行动部署和严整纪律问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5bdb9232ff","index":0,"year":1935,"month":9,"day":18,"articleId":"614cb5e6d2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ae7a8e2929","type":"paragraph","text":"部队的行动部署和严整纪律问题","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"614cb5e6d2"},{"id":"340a886af6","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年9月18日）彭及彭、李：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"614cb5e6d2"},{"id":"54c1dc8bf4","type":"paragraph","text":"一、眠敌守城，哈达铺无敌。第一纵队驻地回、汉民众已大发动，我军纪律尚好，没收敌粮数十万斤、盐二千斤。过大拉山后已无高山溢路。现一纵队驻占扎路、麻子川，纵队部驻鹿原里","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"614cb5e6d2"},{"id":"cb947d9e73","type":"paragraph","text":"二、明（十九）日你们全部开来此间。中央队一科、二科驻鹿原里，二纵队驻旋窝、大草滩，三纵队驻红土坡。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"614cb5e6d2"},{"id":"138e516ff8","type":"paragraph","text":"三、部队严整纪律，没收限于地主及反动派，违者严处。请在明日行军休息时宣布。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"614cb5e6d2"},{"id":"b182fe3275","type":"paragraph","text":"四、缴获手提迫击炮三门，炮弹百余发，尚在大拉。请动员战士带来，可抛弃粮食拿炮弹","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"614cb5e6d2"},{"id":"c2d21b090e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"614cb5e6d2"},{"id":"6819064fc5","type":"paragraph","text":"十八日二十时","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"614cb5e6d2"},{"id":"e4b185b6bf","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东给红军陕甘支队司令员彭德怀及陕甘支队第二纵队司令员彭雪枫、政治委员季富春的电报。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"614cb5e6d2"},{"id":"09ed6e77f4","type":"paragraph","text":"2]眠敌，指当时据守甘肃省眠县的国民党军第三军第十二师唐准源部和新编第十四师鲁大昌部。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"614cb5e6d2"}],"page":{"id":"98f47d2c28","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"614cb5e6d2","start":233,"end":233}}}},"__N_SSG":true}